His Potency the Grand '''Shreeftut''' was the title of the ruler of the [[Ssi-ruuvi Imperium]]. The Shreeftut was elected by both the [[Conclave]] and the [[Elders' Council]], and was required to be a native of [[Lwhekk/Legends|Lwhekk]]. The Shreeftut lived in [[Cree'n'aak Palace]].

